Detailed Description

A category on BkmxAppDel that provides methods which elements in the GUI need for binding.

This is just to keep BkmxAppDel.m from getting too long and cluttered with trivial stuff.

Member Function Documentation

- (NSString*) labelDefaultWebBrowser  

Returns a localized string of text which says "Your Default Browser (XXXXX)".

XXXXX is the name of the user's default web browser.

- (NSString*) labelForKey: (NSString *)  key  

Returns the label for any attribute key for which the receiver responds to -label<Key>.

If the receiver does not respond to -label<Key>, returns a funkified version of the key and logs an error to the console.
